    <h2 class="faq-section-title">Editing your profile</h2>

    <div class="faq-item open">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How do I update my profile with a new job or resume?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Email us at <strong>hello@menoslabs.com</strong> with:
        <br><br>• Your Ask profile URL
        <br>• Your updated resume (paste as text for best results)
        <br>• Any specific changes you'd like made
        <br><br>We'll regenerate your profile and send you a confirmation. Your URL stays the same — nothing breaks for anyone who has your link.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I change my profile theme?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Yes — just email us at <strong>hello@menoslabs.com</strong> with your profile URL and the theme you'd like (Classic, Dark, Bold, or Soft). We'll update it within 24 hours.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I change my URL?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Your URL is permanent and tied to your profile. If you need a different URL (e.g. after a name change), email us and we'll create a new one and set up a redirect from your old URL.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

